Cool bubble. You need
help marketing that?

499
00:19:05,603 --> 00:19:07,229
Only if you
put Jerry on it.

500
00:19:07,313 --> 00:19:08,689
Uh, done.

501
00:19:08,773 --> 00:19:10,149
[ Groans ]

502
00:19:10,274 --> 00:19:12,068
Oh, just make sure
there's enough of him

503
00:19:12,151 --> 00:19:14,070
to go around, huh?
[ Laughs ]

504
00:19:14,111 --> 00:19:16,781
Jerry, you start
on Monday.

505
00:19:16,906 --> 00:19:18,199
Congrats, hon!

506
00:19:18,282 --> 00:19:20,451
[ Groans ]

507
00:19:22,161 --> 00:19:24,664
Sweet Marie
would have loved this.

508
00:19:24,789 --> 00:19:26,207
Who?

509
00:19:26,290 --> 00:19:29,293
[ Rumbling ]

510
00:19:30,670 --> 00:19:33,297
Is there something
wrong with dogs?

511
00:19:33,422 --> 00:19:35,966
I was just trying
to be like you.

512
00:19:36,092 --> 00:19:38,052
I'm so ashamed,
Morty.

513
00:19:38,135 --> 00:19:39,345
Oh, Snowball!

514
00:19:39,470 --> 00:19:41,639
Humans are ashamed
all the time.

515
00:19:41,764 --> 00:19:43,557
You guys
used to be wolves.

516
00:19:43,641 --> 00:19:46,310
Humans, we -- we used
to be sub-hyena.

517
00:19:46,435 --> 00:19:48,979
I think we invented shame
and judgment to cope.

518
00:19:49,105 --> 00:19:51,190
I suppose no creature
is perfect.

519
00:19:51,315 --> 00:19:53,609
Yeah, if we put giraffes
in charge,

520
00:19:53,651 --> 00:19:56,612
they'd just invent, you know,
neck racism, probably.

521
00:19:56,654 --> 00:19:59,615
[ Chuckles ] They <i>do </i>have
those necks, don't they?

522
00:19:59,657 --> 00:20:01,325
Haha. Yeah.

523
00:20:01,450 --> 00:20:05,621
Maybe our species can be
self-conscious together.

524
00:20:08,290 --> 00:20:09,500
[ Beep ]

525
00:20:11,961 --> 00:20:13,671
[ Dog barking ]

526
00:20:14,672 --> 00:20:16,382
Snowball:
Rick? I can explain.

527
00:20:16,507 --> 00:20:18,342
- Easy, buddy.
- Whoa. What happened here?

528
00:20:18,467 --> 00:20:20,136
Four days of civil war.

529
00:20:20,177 --> 00:20:21,429
I never took
a moral stance,

530
00:20:21,512 --> 00:20:23,055
though I resisted
at every turn.

531
00:20:23,139 --> 00:20:25,141
Y-Y-You would have been
so proud of me! Really?

532
00:20:25,182 --> 00:20:28,644
Couldn't pin me down to
nothing. Totally sidelined it.

533
00:20:28,686 --> 00:20:30,646
Hahaha! Good boy.

534
00:20:32,648 --> 00:20:35,317
So, should we just leave it
like this, then, or...?

535
00:20:35,359 --> 00:20:36,819
I feel bad
for Snowball.

536
00:20:36,861 --> 00:20:39,321
He -- He built a monorail,
and now it's all blown up,

537
00:20:39,405 --> 00:20:41,741
a-and everyone's dying.

538
00:20:44,034 --> 00:20:45,578
Well...

539
00:20:49,498 --> 00:20:51,041
Dogs and worms, baby.

540
00:20:51,167 --> 00:20:54,086
I guess every conflict can
be solved with free narcotics.

541
00:20:54,211 --> 00:20:55,379
What a lesson.

542
00:20:55,504 --> 00:20:57,173
Oh, hey.
What happened with Dad?

543
00:20:57,214 --> 00:20:59,091
Did -- Did he
get that job?

544
00:20:59,216 --> 00:21:00,968
[Burps] Advertising
people are perverts.

545
00:21:01,051 --> 00:21:02,511
So no?
Yes.

546
00:21:02,595 --> 00:21:03,637
Alright!

547
00:21:03,721 --> 00:21:10,686
♪♪

548
00:21:11,896 --> 00:21:18,861
♪♪

549
00:21:21,113 --> 00:21:27,828
♪♪

550
00:21:27,912 --> 00:21:32,708
♪♪

551
00:21:36,629 --> 00:21:38,881
So it's all hands
on deck this week.

552
00:21:38,964 --> 00:21:41,842
Jerry! We're throwing darts
at the interns!

553
00:21:41,926 --> 00:21:43,886
Get in here!
Yes, sir!

554
00:21:43,969 --> 00:21:47,223
Boy, I really set
a weird bar for myself.

555
00:21:47,264 --> 00:21:48,724
Sorry. I gotta
wrap this up.

556
00:21:48,808 --> 00:21:51,644
But I wish every client
was as chill as you guys.

557
00:21:51,769 --> 00:21:53,562
I <i>love </i>working
on this account.

558
00:21:53,604 --> 00:21:55,689
Ad dog:
<i>You're the man, Jerry.</i>

559
00:21:55,773 --> 00:21:59,443
<i>- This guy. Sell anything.</i>
- Glug! Ug!

560
00:22:01,070 --> 00:22:02,613
<i>Did you get any of that?</i>

